label: uncl8077
comment: Code specifying the party that is the supplier of the equipment.

values.label: Shipper supplied
values.comment: The transport equipment is supplied by the shipper.

values.label: Carrier supplied
values.comment: The transport equipment is supplied by the carrier.

values.label: Consolidator supplied
values.comment: The equipment is supplied by the consolidator.

values.label: Deconsolidator supplied
values.comment: The equipment is supplied by the deconsolidator.

values.label: Third party supplied
values.comment: The equipment is supplied by a third party.

values.label: Forwarder supplied from a leasing company
values.comment: The equipment is supplied by the forwarder and is taken from a leasing company.

values.label: Forwarder supplied from the railways' pool
values.comment: The equipment is supplied by the forwarder and is taken from a pool established by railway companies.
